    dc:creator "Grebennikov, Vasily V.; Bulirsch, Petr; Magrini, Paolo" ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Discovery of Antireicheia in Cameroon with description of four new species and discussion on phylogeny and distribution of endogean Reicheiina (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Scaritinae: Clivinini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275300>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275301>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275302>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275303> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275300>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Antireicheia demirei sp. nov. from Cameroon (Mt. Oku), holotype (1 – 4) and paratype (5); 1 — habitus, dorsal; 2 – 3 — aedeagus: lateral (2) and ventral (3); 4 – parameres; 5 – stylomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275300/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275301>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 10. Antireicheia hintelmanni sp. nov. from Cameroon (Mt. Oku), holotype (6 – 9) and paratype (10); 6 — habitus, dorsal; 7 – 8 — aedeagus: lateral (7) and ventral (8); 9 – parameres; 10 – stylomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275302>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 16. Antireicheia deuvei sp. nov. from Cameroon (Mt. Bamboutos), holotype (11 – 15) and paratype (16); 11 — habitus, dorsal; 12 – 13 — aedeagus: lateral (12) and ventral (13); 14 – parameres; 15 — urite; 16 – stylomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275303>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 22. Antireicheia camerounensis sp. nov. from Cameroon (Bafut, Nguemba forest), holotype (17 – 21) and paratype (22); 17 — habitus, dorsal; 18 – 19 — aedeagus: lateral (18) and ventral (19); 20 — parameres; 21 — urite; 22 – stylomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

